<h4>Notices</h4>

Notices are things a visitor should be aware of, but not emergency.
<br>
<p>
They are displayed as a bulleted list of items, which each line in the text field (separated by carriage returns) being one bulleted item.
<br />
You cannot use html code in here, as the special characters (like &gt;) will be converted to entities.
</p>

<p>Notices are displayed on the one-page summary page, on the notices page of the everything report, and on the notices panel of the rotation sequence.
</p>
